="92">Figs 32</figureCitation>
<figureCitation id="2FA131A5AAB679E7851CD317AAE098C6" captionStart="Figures 99–102" captionStartId="F15" captionText="Figures 99 - 102. Lateral and dorsal habitus images of Zygopini. Scale bars = 2 mm unless otherwise specified. 99 a-b Peltophorus polymitus suffusus [ASUHIC 0016837]. 100 a-b Phileas granulatus [ARTSYS 0000528]. 101 a-b Philenis flavipes [ASUHIC 0065102]; scale bar for 101 a = 1 mm 102 a-b Zygops vitticollis [ASUHIC 0086634]; scale bar for 102 b = 5 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.683.12080.figures99–102" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/143840" pageId="41" pageNumber="92">, 100</figureCitation>
